   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>To Ptolemaios also called Sarapion, secretary of the city, from Papontos, son of Alypos and Taras and grandson of Papontos, from the city of Oxyrhynchus. My father Alypos, son of Papontos and Teironeia, from the same city, an adult without a trade, registered in the quarter of the gooseherds, died in the past month of Choiak [- - -]</ab>
         </div>
